        <!-- Optional: URL for more information about this update -->
        <url>https://github.com/SmartmindTech/SM_Estratoos_plugin/releases/tag/v1.7.27</url>

        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 1.7.27 - Fix Role Detection & Add Role Filter</h3>
            <p><strong>Two improvements to the token management page</strong></p>

            <h4>1. Fixed Role Detection</h4>
            <p>Role badges now correctly detect teachers and students:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Before:</strong> Only checked system-level roles (many users showed as "Other")</li>
                <li><strong>After:</strong> Checks ALL role assignments (system, category, and course level)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Teachers and students enrolled in courses are now properly identified.</p>

            <h4>2. Role Filter Dropdown</h4>
            <p>Added a new filter dropdown on the token management page:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Filter tokens by role: Manager, Teacher, Student, or Other</li>
                <li>Works alongside existing Company and Service filters</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
